sentence: In Alaska, state Republican Party leaders have endorsed a primary challenge to the state's incumbent senator, Lisa Murkowski, while GOP officials in Wyoming have disowned their incumbent congresswoman, Rep. Liz Cheney.
title: GOP plunges into season of self-hate' that will rewire the party
